  <title>Update the keyring password</title>

  <p>The password to unlock your <link xref="keyring">keyring</link> can
  be updated at any time.</p>

  <steps>
    <title>To update the password for a password keyring:</title>
      <item>
	<p>Select the password keyring from the list, under
	<app>Passwords</app>, on the left side panel.</p>
      </item>
      <item>
	<p>Right click on the selected password keyring and select
	<gui>Change Password</gui>.</p>
      </item>
      <item>
	<p>Type your old password to authenticate yourself and press
	<gui style="button">Continue</gui>.</p>
      </item>
      <item>
	<p>In the new dialog, type your new password, retype it to confirm the
	new password and press the <gui style="button">Continue</gui> button to
	finish.</p>
      </item>
  </steps>

